title: Texas National Guard soldier remains missing after helping rescue two migrants suspected of drug trafficking - CNN
content:
1. Texas National Guard soldier remains missing after helping rescue two migrants suspected of drug trafficking  CNN

description: A Texas Army National Guard soldier who went missing Friday during a rescue mission along the border with Mexico has not yet been found, according to a release from the Texas Military Department (TMD).
